If you are entering into this Agreement on behalf of a business or other legal entity, you represent that you have the authority to bind such entity to this Agreement, in which case the terms, “you“，or “your” shall refer to such entity.
Please read this Agreement carefully before installing or using the Software. By Clicking the “Agree” Button or by installing and using the Software, you
(a)	acknowledge that you have read and understand this Agreement; 
(b)	represent that you are 18 years of age or older/of legal age to enter into a binding Agreement; and
(c)	accept this Agreement and agree that you are legally bound by its terms.
If you do not agree to the terms of this Agreement, you are not entitled to install the Software.


